# my-pro-project

> A professional, modular, and ready-to-use Python starter project.  
> Features CLI, tests, logging, and CI/CD workflow integration.

---

## 🚀 Project Status
- **Status:** Development ready
- **Language:** Python
- **License:** MIT

---

## 🔍 Features
- Professional CLI tool
- Modular code structure
- Logging and verbose mode
- Ready-to-run tests
- GitHub Actions CI

---

## 🛠️ Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<username>/my-pro-project.git
cd my-pro-project
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate   # macOS/Linux
.venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt  # optional
